            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> carrot ribbons</strong>, <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong>,<strong> sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, <strong>sesame croutons</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped mint </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the hoisin dressing and give it a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>bánh mì-style salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1634718299064-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
