        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free chick'n is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
