    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pulled meat-free chick'n</strong> over the <strong>bánh mì-style salad</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped mint </strong>and <strong>coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
